item.title: Jackass Star Ryan Dunn Dies In Fatal Car Crash
item.description:
Jackass Star Ryan Dunn Dies In Fatal Car Crash
Follow Twitter: http://www.twitter.com/Hollyscoop Fan Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/Hollyscoop Hollyscoop.com gives the scoop on the sad news of Jackass star Ryan Dunn who died in a fatal car crash. Images by Wenn.com. Video hosted by Nora Gasparian / Twitter: http://twitter.com/NoraGasparian Ryan Dunn of Jackass fame was involved in a fatal car crash in Pennsylvania early Monday morning. Dunn and an unidentified person both died in the crash, which happened at Route 322 and New Street in West Goshen Township. The crash happened around 3 a.m. No word on who was driving the car, but Dunn's Porsche caught on fire in the crash and, hours later, a tow truck arrived on scene to remove the vehicle. Bam Margera's mother confirmed that Dunn had passed away from the crash. Hours before his death, Dunn posted a Twitter photo of he and two friends drinking. Dunn has appeared in all three Jackass movies, including the latest one, Jackass 3D. He also had one season of his own show, Homewrecker, where he helped practical joke victims get revenge.  Details are still unfolding. May Dunn rest in peace.
